d 1<b>. Meanwhile, place broccoli in Varoma dish, season with salt and ¼ tsp black pepper and set aside."},{"content":"Add potatoes to mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>."},{"content":"Add remaining ¼ tsp black pepper, stock paste and water, place Varoma in position, secure Varoma lid and cook <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside."},{"content":"Add lamb’s lettuce, cream, sugar, lemon juice and Worcestershire sauce to mixing bowl and blend <b>2 min\/speed 5<b>-<strong>10, increasing speed gradually from speed 5 to speed 10.<\/strong> Adjust seasoning to taste. Serve soup as a starter and broccoli with olive sauce as a side dish, along with a main dish of your choice."}],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","45m","6 portions"]}